article.headline: UC Davis 65, UC Riverside 58
article.story: DAVIS, Calif. -- Mark Payne had 16 points and 10 rebounds to help UC Davis beat UC Riverside 65-58 on Thursday night. Joe Harden had 12 points and seven rebounds and Dominic Calegari added 11 points and four rebounds for the Aggies (6-9, 1-1 Big West). Kyle Austin had 17 points and five rebounds and Aaron Scott added 11 points and eight rebounds for the Highlanders (9-5, 2-1). The Highlanders overcame a 12-point deficit to tie the Aggies at 44 on a 3-pointer by Javon Borum midway through the second half. The Aggies took control the lead for good at 57-56 on a basket by Vince Oliver with 2:32 left.
